<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10438004>
    dc:description "FIGURE 57. Collected specimens (A–C), and distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas (D, E). Nepomorpha from Rio de Janeiro state. A–B. Naucoridae, Limnocoris. A. Limnocoris acutalis, male from Cantagalo (−21.9720, −42.3931). B. Limnocoris pusillus, male from São Fidélis (−21.6106, −41.8078). C. Notonectidae, Martarega bentoi, male from Itaocara (−21.6431, −42.0274). D. Limnocoris acutalis (red) and Limnocoris pusillus (yellow). E. Martarega bentoi. Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records. Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10438004/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

